{"tid":1085450,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"見到上個分享最鍾意嘅一張相，我又想分享。","createTime":"2019-03-31T07:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T08:47:50.000Z","uid":25050,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e40f07dcde4abaf035ee10f1f0d8d788b7958861","tid":1085450,"uid":25050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"由於都鍾意影吓相 拋吓磚<br />\n<br />\n朝早六點嘅大尾篤<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LEmMJbs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLEmMJbs.png&h=913e6994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下午六點嘅南生圍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rciCPRP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrciCPRP.png&h=dadc48b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去塔門瞓唔慣又凍 坐係舊大石度等日出<br />\n六點半到八點半 不過影得好差<br />\n不過第一次見到個紅圈真係好吸引<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30PKuTT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30PKuTT.png&h=df4d57bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEPyodW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaEPyodW.png&h=5ec7b3d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWbEiNi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWbEiNi.png&h=4188241b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分別兩次去小蠔灣釣魚 改吓啲色幾正<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CQ2gCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CQ2gCx.png&h=073900f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/31/150513_a92471b959551326f6b6dccfe4e403c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F31%2F150513_a92471b959551326f6b6dccfe4e403c0.png&h=752bdad0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/31/150600_2151d10bf3ecc94e5fa5e5aff0d6b7c5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F31%2F150600_2151d10bf3ecc94e5fa5e5aff0d6b7c5.png&h=c735c14c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返中山嗰陣係車度影<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHiCP0P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHiCP0P.png&h=628e6219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用iphone6s影 影得差唔好屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0199d90fd9286c5205492f3fc35ba662e10937be","tid":1085450,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:59:39.000Z","msg":"最尾果張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a6d2804863085e977ecba23599b19c5235e2d1","tid":1085450,"uid":25050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0199d90fd9286c5205492f3fc35ba662e10937be","tid":1085450,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:59:39.000Z","msg":"最尾果張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T08:07:46.000Z","msg":"我見到咁光忍唔住影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後都無再見過咁嘅太陽"},{"pid":"3ccb2f73e34d1250dae66093b4ffd47ace21500b","tid":1085450,"uid":11116,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"支持樓主分享<br />\n雖然 d 相真係有d 麻麻<br />\n不過可能手機hdr渣渣 (最後個光爛晒一達達）<br />\n不如買部相機 入坑窮三代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e842bb2d5455a17ff4ae191c6783c02d9a6b8341","tid":1085450,"uid":25050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ccb2f73e34d1250dae66093b4ffd47ace21500b","tid":1085450,"uid":11116,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"支持樓主分享<br />\n雖然 d 相真係有d 麻麻<br />\n不過可能手機hdr渣渣 (最後個光爛晒一達達）<br />\n不如買部相機 入坑窮三代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T19:02:29.000Z","msg":"有諗過買部 不過真係會窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797aa9e36173581b084d56d88da94fee5793421